reviewText:
Beautiful & trippy visuals set to trancy techno... highly recommend if you're into the electronic music scene.
A feast for the senses.

I have a few DVD from this AV studio. Altho this is not there strongest DVD, it is still good. Visuals are very good. The music is just ok. This is a good DVD to use at a party or if your a DJ. Over all good DVD. (c=
